MAXLAMBDA > 0 and recouple() update

update_add_phonon() and update_remove_phonon() could avoid using diagram_clone() -- which is quite expensive --
by calculating the weightratio without creating a new diagram. Then we add add/remove a line only if the update
has been accepted.

